title: *PATREON PREVIEW* Dead Podcasters Society
description:
O Throw Gang! My Throw Gang! This week, Jimmy and Larry are carping the goddamn motherfucking diem, living life not just to the fullest, but in the moment as they breakdown Baroque Boyz, new merch, parties disguised as photoshoots, near-death experiences, Lil Uzi Vert’s new forehead diamond, body modification, Super Bowl Sunday, Girl Scout cookies, ‘The Little Rascals’, HBO’s ‘Fake Famous’ documentary and much more.
 
For more Throwing Fits, check us out on Patreon: www.patreon.com/throwingfits.
